\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3105192 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 That's where she went home for you being born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1142424 LP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 Yes. Mm hm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3105192 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 Did she do any jobs before she was married?
