\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3105192 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 This was in Falmouth?
