\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1142424 LP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 Yes. Yes, I suppose and - by the time - well I was only fourteen you see when I went to -
