Yes. We used - we were friends with the - friendly with the manager of Lennards Mr Rees, and - mum used to get most of - shoes there, I was pretty heavy on shoes too. I can remember wearing some with patches on them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3105192 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 Cobbleers would do patches then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1142424 LP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 Yes. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3105192 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 Did you ever have any secondhand clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1142424 LP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 I don't think so, I don't remember having any.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3105192 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 Nobody in the family would hand them down?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1142424 LP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 No, there's - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3105192 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 Did father ever help mother with any of the household jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1142424 LP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 
Well he wasn't - the only - father was very good at cooking if necessary, he - he could fry and he could roast and he - that sort of thing, but - he wasn't much on housework itself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3105192 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 When would he consider it necessary then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1142424 LP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 
Oh if mum was ill. Yes. That was later - not - it was a little while be - while we were still at Barripper Road, one Christ - just coming up to Christmas, about six weeks before Christmas, mum burnt her hand very badly 
with boiling fat and - well she was - she had her arm in a sling until after Christmas, the doctor said, well John, what are you going to do about your Christmas dinner? Oh, he said, you needn't worry about my Christmas dinner, we'll have our Christmas di
n
ner, I'll - I'll promise that. And we did, we had our roast goose and daddy roasted it, and Christ - and I did most of the cooking - of the cake and that sort of business with mother standing at the side. I learnt to cook then. I was about - thirteen, tha
t must have been about - no - it was before the war, so - and the war was in 1914 so it must have been perhaps 1912 or somewhere like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3105192 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 That stands out in your memory?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1142424 LP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 Oh - yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3105192 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 Would he do anything about fires?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1142424 LP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 Well he would if - if - well again if - mum was poorly or anything and wasn't - up to it, but in the normal way he didn't.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3105192 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 What about kindling or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1142424 LP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 Oh sometimes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3105192 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 House decorating or repairs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1142424 LP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 Oh yes - no, I think he used to help with papering, that sort of thing. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3105192 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 And painting?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1142424 LP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3105192 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 Any improvements to the house can you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1142424 LP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 No you see it wasn't our own house and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3105192 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 This was at Barripper Road?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1142424 LP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 Yes, Barripper Road. And - he didn't - we didn't sort of - we weren't responsible for that sort of thing and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3105192 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 It didn't come up to be considered?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1142424 LP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3105192 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 Cleaning I suppose would be the women's job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1142424 LP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3105192 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 You and mother and the help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1142424 LP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3105192 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 Did he ever read to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1142424 LP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 
Oh yes. He used - and - yes, I - - one thing I used to always want to be - want him to tell me about - the big ships when he went to South Africa, and tell me about South Africa and so on. I was always very interested in that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3105192 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 He would tell you stories of his own experiences?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1142424 LP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 
Yes. So - I - I can't remember them now really but - I remember climbing into bed on a Sunday morning, daddy, tell me about the big ships. I can remember that. Mm. That was when - well must have been quite small then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3105192 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 Do you remember him ever telling you anything about the actual campaign?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1142424 LP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 No. No. I believe he - I - I often think there are so many things I'd like to have - to have asked him if I could ask him now you know.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3105192 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 Of course that was all over before you were born.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1142424 LP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3105192 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 So it would all be from him that you would know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1142424 LP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3105192 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 Did he ever help mother with you like dressing or undressing you or anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1142424 LP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 Oh yes. Yes, sometimes, mm hm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3105192 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 Bath}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2236071\charrsid813743 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 
night or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1142424 LP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 No, I don't think he - took part in that, you see, we - there was only me so it wasn't like a big family to be bathed and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3105192 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 The need didn't arise really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1142424 LP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3105192 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 Did he ever take you out without your mother, like for walks or things like that
