\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1142424 LP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16601870\charrsid813743 Well I did later on when he was - when I was old enough. But not in - 1911 you see I wasn't old enough to do anything for him then.
