Well - he - first - while he was convalescent I used to push him out in a bath chair then, but I mean he didn't take up his work - again for a long time because he was 
so - bad - very ill you see he took a long time to convalesce - and - it was in 19 - 21, that I helped most when I was waiting to go to college. And then I did - actually did quite a lot of his bookwork for him as Relieving Officer.
